definition: radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 4)/see 撇[pie3]
testosterone/also written 睾甾酮[gao1 zai1 tong2]
testosterone/abbr. for 睾丸甾酮[gao1 wan2 zai1 tong2]

sentences.english: Objective To explore the clinical value of B-Type ultrasonic diagnosis of clonorchiosis.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨利用B型超声诊断华支睾吸虫病的临床价值。

sentences.english: Epidemic Status and Countermeasure of Clonorchiasis in Guangxi;
sentences.chinese: 提出了“成瘾型”流行区华支睾吸虫病的防制对策。

sentences.english: Objective To survey the Clonorchis sinensis infection status in Shuikou Town.
sentences.chinese: 目的了解开平市水口镇人体华支睾吸虫感染状况。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the application of B ultrasonic examination on the diagnosis of clonorchiasis .
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨B超在华支睾吸虫病诊断中的应用价值。

sentences.english: It had no cross-reaction with Clonorchiasis.
sentences.chinese: 与华枝睾吸虫病无交叉反应。

sentences.english: To investigate the application of B-ultrasonic examination on the diagnosis of clonorchiasis.
sentences.chinese: 探讨B超在华支睾吸虫病诊断中的应用价值。

sentences.english: Objective To study the character and treatment of clonorchiasis sinensis combined with cholangitis.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨华支睾吸虫病并胆道感染的特点与治疗。

sentences.english: Conclusion B ultrasonic examination is valuable to the diagnosis of clonorchiasis.
sentences.chinese: 结论B超诊断华支睾吸虫病具有重要的价值。

sentences.english: Meanwhile, love-struck women get a testosterone boost.
sentences.chinese: 但恋爱的妇女反而得到睾甾酮助力。

sentences.english: A new way of diagnosis to the clonorchiasis was exploited.
sentences.chinese: 为华支睾吸虫病提供了新的诊断途径。

sentences.english: Cross-reactivity was seen in 1 case of clonorchiasis sinensis by both the methods.
sentences.chinese: 均发现1例华支睾吸虫病患者的交叉反应。

sentences.english: The paper reports the results of epidemiology of clonorchiasis sinensis in Sichuan Province.
sentences.chinese: 本文报告了四川省华支睾吸虫病流行病学调查结果。

sentences.english: To find out the infection status of Clonorchis sinensis metacercariae in freshwater fish in Baicheng region.
sentences.chinese: 了解白城地区华支睾吸虫第二中间宿主感染情况。

sentences.english: Objective To study the infection of freshwater fishes with the encysted metacercaria of Clonorchis sinensis.
sentences.chinese: 目的了解淡水鱼华支睾吸虫囊蚴感染情况。
